{
  "texts": [
    "After each task, they were asked to provide feedback.",
    "Then, after completing all tasks, the participants were posed several open questions about the system's benefits, risks, and barriers to adoption.",
    "Finally, demographic information, such as age, gender, and role, was collected.",
    "We recruited N = 9 participants from a detergent factory, of which n = 4 were managers (P1-4), and n = 5 were operators (P5-9).",
    "Of the nine participants, n = 3 were women, and n = 6 were men."
  ]
}